---
// About section with professional summary
---

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lead">
          I am a senior architecture and technology strategy leader with over 20 years of experience
          driving transformational data and software solutions across pharmaceutical, healthcare, and
          enterprise sectors.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently serving as an <strong>Advisor (R5) in Advanced Intelligence</strong> at
          <strong>Eli Lilly & Company</strong>, I lead the Software Engineering chapter, pushing
          capabilities in cloud architecture, machine learning engineering, DevOps, UI/UX, and data
          visualization.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans from architecting the <strong>BioNova drug discovery project</strong> enabling
          de novo molecular design on high-performance computing clusters, to implementing compliance
          monitoring solutions for enterprise risk management. I've introduced continuous delivery
          patterns that accelerate time to value for dozens of projects across clinical, laboratory,
          medical affairs, and financial domains.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe in mentoring teams on AWS best practices, software development excellence, and
          enterprise integration strategies. Throughout my career, I've been recognized with a Top 100
          Innovator award, 3 Innovation awards, and 2 Techy awards.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-number">20+</div>
          <div class="highlight-label">Years Experience</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-number">6</div>
          <div class="highlight-label">Awards at Lilly</div>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-card">
          <div class="highlight-number">100+</div>
          <div class="highlight-label">Projects Delivered</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl) var(--spacing-md);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    color: var(--color-text);
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-title::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
    margin: var(--spacing-md) auto 0;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .highlight-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .highlight-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .highlight-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .about-highlights {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .highlight-card {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 120px;
    }

    .highlight-number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .lead {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
  }
</style>
